"height:126px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Desa Labota</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/ew5z28p0y5zj83t/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Labota-1.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:210px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/7vnzdixawdm606h/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Labota-2.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:210px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/t3wypky9riu349c/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Labota-3.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:210px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/pauf5vxkyr5hpu4/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Labota-4.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:173px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Desa Lalampu</strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/3lxkmqe47mli8u7/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Lalampu-1.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:211px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/w234pp07mgx7y8u/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Lalampu-2.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:206px; width:300px\" /></strong></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Desa Le Le</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/m4wk4z2y34e9kzo/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Le%20Le.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:147px; width:300px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Desa Makarti Jaya</strong></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/zan6mojm96zdcbd/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20Makarti%20Jaya-1.jpg?dl=1\" style=\"height:212px; width:300px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Desa Padabaho</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/buoamnkpy339rxo/Tabel%20Industri%20dan%20Perdagangan%20Desa%20P